1625
01:34:43,920 --> 01:34:45,460
 Ali ako možeš napraviti

1626
01:34:45,460 --> 01:34:47,140
 da ozdraviš na bolje

1627
01:34:47,140 --> 01:34:48,540
 ko kaže

1628
01:34:48,540 --> 01:34:49,960
 da ne možeš napraviti

1629
01:34:49,960 --> 01:34:51,620
 i da potruješ narode

1630
01:34:51,620 --> 01:34:52,460
 na taj način.

1631
01:34:52,460 --> 01:34:53,180
 Da.

1632
01:34:53,180 --> 01:34:54,360
 I tu se znači

1633
01:34:54,360 --> 01:34:56,180
